---
import PageMeta from "../components/PageMeta.astro";
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout>
  <PageMeta title="About Me | ${SITE_TITLE}" slot="meta" />
  <section slot="main">
    <article>
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Jane Smith, an experienced ML engineer and software engineer
        based in XYZ City. I am passionate about leveraging artificial
        intelligence and machine learning to build intelligent and innovative
        solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently, I am working on the V2 of a time management system that
        utilizes machine learning algorithms to analyze user behavior and
        provide personalized productivity recommendations. This project has
        given me valuable insights into developing scalable and efficient ML
        solutions.
      </p>
    </article>

    <section>
      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>Machine Learning</li>
        <li>Deep Learning</li>
        <li>TensorFlow</li>
        <li>PyTorch</li>
        <li>Data Analysis</li>
        <li>Software Development</li>
        <li>Git</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <p>
        Over the years, I have worked on various ML projects ranging from image
        recognition to natural language processing. I have hands-on experience
        with popular ML frameworks such as TensorFlow and PyTorch, and have
        successfully implemented models in real-world scenarios.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am passionate about solving complex problems and optimizing algorithms
        for performance. I thrive in collaborative environments and enjoy
        working with cross-functional teams to deliver exceptional results.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Looking for New Opportunities</h2>
      <p>
        I am currently seeking new opportunities where I can apply my skills and
        expertise in ML engineering and software development. I am eager to join
        a team that is passionate about pushing the boundaries of AI and
        building innovative solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any exciting projects or job opportunities, I would love to
        connect and discuss how I can contribute. Please feel free to reach out
        to me via email or through the contact form on my website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any inquiries or would like to discuss potential
        collaboration opportunities, feel free to reach out to me via email or
        through the contact form on my website. I am always open to exciting new
        projects and partnerships.
      </p>
      <p>Email: jane.smith@example.com</p>
    </section>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
